OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA blustery day, with showery
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, these could be
OL,7,Fheavy at times, before easing later. A
OL,8,Ffew bright or sunny spells possible,
OL,9,Fmainly during the late afternoon.
OL,10,FFeeling mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA bright end to the day with
OL,13,Fsunny spells giving way to clear skies
OL,14,Fovernight. Turning cloudier over the
OL,15,Fhills later in the night and feeling
OL,16,Frather chilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
