OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA chilly start on Saturday
OL,6,Fand soon clouding over from the west
OL,7,Fwith outbreaks of rain arriving.
OL,8,FTurning increasingly windy as Storm
OL,9,FDave arrives with gales and severe
OL,10,Fgales developing.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,13,Fbut blustery on Easter Sunday, with
OL,14,Fscattered showers. Winds easing
OL,15,Fleaving a drier, brighter, and warmer
OL,16,FEaster Monday. Settled initially on
OL,17,FTuesday, but clouding over with rain
OL,18,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
